{"tid":1355804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六四「屠夫」李鵬去世　89年宣佈戒嚴上演血腥鎮壓","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:58:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"366536133c55ca6fe3eee495316d321a28b2cf9e","tid":1355804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"新華社報道，國務院前總理李鵬於7月22日去世，終年90歲。<br />\n<br />\n新華社通報，中國共產黨中央委員會、中華人民共和國全國人民代表大會常務委員會、中華人民共和國國務院、中國人民政治協商會議全國委員會沉痛宣告：中國共產黨的優秀黨員，久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，傑出的無產階級革命家、政治家，黨和國家的卓越領導人，中國共產黨第十二屆中央政治局委員、中央書記處書記，第十三屆、十四屆、十五屆中央政治局常委，國務院原總理，第九屆全國人民代表大會常務委員會委員長李鵬同志，因病醫治無效，於2019年7月22日晚上11時11分在北京逝世。"},{"pid":"ff1748f2cc6af5d25af7fbb5ada253176c80e29f","tid":1355804,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"李鵬祖籍湖北，出生於上海法租界，畢業於蘇聯莫斯科動力學院水力發電系。1945年加入中國共產黨，曾任電力工業部部長、國家教育委員會主任、國務院副總理、國務院總理和全國人大常委會委員長等重要職務，為中共前主要領導人之一。<br />\n<br />\n1989年4月15日，前中共中央總書記胡耀邦去逝，北京大學生與市民在天安門廣場舉辦悼念活動。民眾後來提出不滿政府貪污及各種社會問題，無數學生及市民長期聚集天安門廣場進行抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n同年5月19日，李鵬在電視上發表措詞強硬的「五&middot;一九講話」，引起首都大學生不滿，聚集在天安門廣場上示威的大學生表示更強烈的抗議。5月20日，李鵬以總理身份簽署國務院令，決定自5月20日起在北京部份地區實施戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n6月4日凌晨，解放軍在天安門實施清場行動，其間更開槍進行武力鎮壓，釀成數以百計民眾學生死亡，事件震驚中外。外界認為，李鵬是六四事件其中一名「屠夫」。"},{"pid":"eeac8a77b91dd98e97b0eae915a129abfa6e8a35","tid":1355804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190723/59854438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59854438&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f99b1c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59854438&h=f832c1ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190723/59854438</a>"},{"pid":"95794ef7abdd163c7f82ed72e7ff0544e1845d93","tid":1355804,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEFexkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEFexkY.png&h=c2871d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0d6f51fc7ba5fc0bbceff54dbe1ac89511f7882","tid":1355804,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZRtzxmL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRtzxmL.png&h=b988eb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUgM7U6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUgM7U6.png&h=2f708bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnmYez7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnmYez7.png&h=c06cfceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtufgOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtufgOt.png&h=9325ccd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2FaP8t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2FaP8t.png&h=72859691&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbojJtt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbojJtt.png&h=54bff366&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZgtBOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZgtBOu.png&h=cf68719f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"543374dee528ca8603bbabf548ca5db5e4508f54","tid":1355804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}